{"tid":1699812,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"領展將發放尚德停車場更多閉路電視片段","createTime":"2019-11-08T07:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T10:19:49.000Z","uid":12006,"like":95,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"344db9794012b46ab3d18fac5294fdce3087fe8b","tid":1699812,"uid":12006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"領展對科技大學學生周梓樂離世感到婉惜及難過，向家人及親友致以深切慰問。領展表示，明白公眾非常關注周梓樂在尚德停車場墮樓事件，星期三公開最可能拍攝到與事件相關的10個片段，由於外界對事發經過仍有疑問，領展計劃盡快發放更多閉路電視片段。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，由於片段眾多，需時分段複製，但不會編輯片段，為保障個人私隱及遵從法例要求，領展在發放片段前需將片段內出現的公眾人士面容以電腦效果遮蓋，正全力進行有關工作，將分批發布，公司亦會繼續配合警方調查， 提供一切所需協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1205031&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1205031%26csid%3D261_341&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUq7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=a56d9e85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1205031&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"e7bba94f4434a1573f533a2f51ebee6916930ee3","tid":1699812,"uid":12006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:40:42.000Z","msg":"會放更多CCTV片"},{"pid":"c2df5ecfc3dd222e3c8281eb798c431c0acb5633","tid":1699812,"uid":111898,"like":6,"dislike":17,"score":-11,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:42:36.000Z","msg":"咁點解之前唔放呀"},{"pid":"370f3a6652b74aab7a0f3f44cbcc19b6cce118b8","tid":1699812,"uid":45925,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:44:39.000Z","msg":"而家放得出嚟，d狗都睇過曬冇料到先比你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b8e60277f56531d9dee20293c88472071e71be","tid":1699812,"uid":30988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"繼續。有好過無"},{"pid":"6edbb4e3ab02b988cac37d37cabe45873bc75656","tid":1699812,"uid":53027,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"c2df5ecfc3dd222e3c8281eb798c431c0acb5633","tid":1699812,"uid